272
00:15:49,380 --> 00:15:52,640
No, I'm not saying aliens are scary.

273
00:15:54,180 --> 00:15:55,140
Tsumiuta?

274
00:15:55,570 --> 00:15:57,390
Or Zaika?

275
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:00,390
"Wealth"?

276
00:16:00,390 --> 00:16:02,310
I'll take a look at it later.

277
00:16:02,310 --> 00:16:04,740
Anyway, you've got a job, Selty.

278
00:16:04,740 --> 00:16:06,960
It's from Shiki-san of the Awakusu Group again.

279
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,610
It's not a very pleasant job though.

280
00:16:08,610 --> 00:16:09,870
Will you do it?

281
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,400
Another delivery?

282
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:14,220
Yeah.

283
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:17,740
Well, you have to get the stolen goods back first though.

284
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:20,010
I have no idea what the goods are.

285
00:16:20,010 --> 00:16:22,460
I think it's better not to know.

286
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:23,750
I know.

287
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:25,860
So, about the goods...

288
00:16:25,860 --> 00:16:28,320
The thief's on the run.

289
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:32,580
We have an idea on his location, so we should be able to corner him easily.

290
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:34,950
Roger.

291
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:41,930
The slasher has been quite active lately, so be careful.

292
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,940
