294
00:16:44,710 --> 00:16:47,050
Looks like he appeared again.

295
00:16:47,050 --> 00:16:49,690
He just slashes people without killing them.

296
00:16:49,690 --> 00:16:52,240
Well, you can't call him the strongest then.

297
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:54,700
The strongest in this city would be...

298
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:56,570
Simon from Russia Sushi.

299
00:16:56,570 --> 00:17:00,080
What about the informant that moved to Shinjuku?

300
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,580
Orihara Izaya.

301
00:17:01,580 --> 00:17:04,000
Then it has to be that guy...

302
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,830
Heiwajima Shizuo!

303
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,810
The strongest color gang?

304
00:17:10,810 --> 00:17:12,650
Dude, it's the Dollars.

305
00:17:12,650 --> 00:17:14,250
They don't have a color.

306
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:17,380
Those peeps in yellow were the big shots until last year though.

307
00:17:17,380 --> 00:17:18,280
Yellow?

308
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:20,810
Yeah, the Yellow Napkins.

309
00:17:20,810 --> 00:17:25,970
But I heard that they fought the Blue Squares last year, and they wrecked each other.

310
00:17:25,970 --> 00:17:29,250
Dude, I heard they revived recently.

311
00:17:29,860 --> 00:17:32,400
Please don't stop the orders from comin'!

312
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:36,070
