00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:40,930
The yellow guys?

317
00:17:40,930 --> 00:17:42,470
Oh, so you noticed them.

318
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:43,830
By yellow, you don't happen to mean...

319
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:44,790
Yellow Snapkins!

320
00:17:44,790 --> 00:17:46,020
You mean "Yellow Napkins."

321
00:17:46,020 --> 00:17:47,200
Yep, yep, them.

322
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:48,920
That was Hermes, right?

323
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:53,330
No, they were annihilated in the fight with the Blue Squares.

324
00:17:53,330 --> 00:17:55,040
Oh, right.

325
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:57,890
I heard their boss went AWOL.

326
00:17:58,700 --> 00:18:00,550
Welcome!

327
00:18:05,580 --> 00:18:08,100
Could you tell me about the Dollars?

328
00:18:08,810 --> 00:18:11,900
One of my friends wants to join them, and I want to stop him.

329
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:15,530
Why are you asking us?

330
00:18:15,530 --> 00:18:18,240
There's no one else I can ask.

331
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:21,570
He can't just go to Orihara Izaya obviously.

332
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:28,980
We don't know that much about them either,

333
00:18:28,980 --> 00:18:31,350
but we'll tell you everything we know.

334
00:18:32,420 --> 00:18:35,820
Sometimes I feel like I'm getting sucked in by this town.

335
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:40,160
But Mikado, I won't let you go to that side.

336
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,730
Mikado?!

337
00:18:58,320 --> 00:18:58,740
Sorry.

338
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:01,610
That won't work, bro.

339
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:05,660
We're Yellow Napkins, ya see?

340
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:07,950
Yagiri-kun!

341
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:11,790
Huh?

342
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:14,170
That's not Harima Mika.

343
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:18,970
I don't know who you are, but please don't get in the way of our elopement of love.

344
00:19:18,970 --> 00:19:21,090
