347
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:34,270
Kida-kun.

348
00:19:40,330 --> 00:19:42,490
Are you guys really from the Yellow Napkins?

349
00:19:43,090 --> 00:19:44,160
Isn't that obvious, Sherlock?

350
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:46,230
I'm asking because I don't know.

351
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:48,220
You fucking...

352
00:19:48,220 --> 00:19:50,160
K-Kida-kun!

353
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:54,130
Oh man, Mikado-kun... Why are you here?

354
00:20:02,820 --> 00:20:05,010
M-Monster!

355
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:08,970
Let's go!

356
00:20:38,260 --> 00:20:40,630
