362
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:57,840
Maybe this time I can meet her without running away.

363
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:58,400
Come in.

364
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:01,460
That's what I really think.

365
00:21:03,730 --> 00:21:06,190
I didn't think you'd come,

366
00:21:08,770 --> 00:21:09,950
Izaya-san.

367
00:21:09,950 --> 00:21:10,910
Hey.

368
00:21:12,930 --> 00:21:14,670
How's he doing?

369
00:21:14,670 --> 00:21:17,420
He visits me from time to time.

370
00:21:18,210 --> 00:21:20,090
He was just here.

371
00:21:32,300 --> 00:21:33,100
I'm home.

372
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:38,150
Haruna, did you eat already?

373
00:21:38,510 --> 00:21:39,480
Haruna.

374
00:21:48,070 --> 00:21:51,330
Oh, I blacklisted that spammer.

375
00:21:51,330 --> 00:21:53,080
Looks like it's gonna be peaceful here.

376
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,750
I hope so.

377
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:59,250
Oh yeah. I heard that some of the Yellow Napkins
got their asses kicked by the slasher yesterday.

378
00:21:59,250 --> 00:22:01,170
