387
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:27,660
G-Good morning, Sonohara-san.

388
00:22:27,660 --> 00:22:29,240
Good morning.
I just realized this,

389
00:22:30,020 --> 00:22:33,630
but I really like our relationship the way it is now.

390
00:22:33,630 --> 00:22:35,990
One day I'll connect the dots,

391
00:22:35,990 --> 00:22:39,130
and unveil the picture that's currently invisible to us.

392
00:22:39,130 --> 00:22:43,890
I believe that our relationship will stay the same.

393
00:24:15,430 --> 00:24:16,640
Dollars?

394
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:18,560
